{%- comment -%}
  Sahha Daily marquee — ported from the live site's <Marquee>. A slim, infinitely
  scrolling bilingual trust bar that sits above the header. Items are duplicated
  once so the -50% translate loops seamlessly; the duplicate set is aria-hidden.

  Edit the phrases below (one <span class="sahha-mq__item"> per phrase). Pause on
  hover; animation disabled under prefers-reduced-motion. REM ×1.6 for Dawn's 10px
  root (see memory design-port-sahha).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign items = section.settings.items | default: '🌿 100% verified originals · بضاعة أصلية مضمونة|🇬🇧 Directly sourced from Europe · من أوروبا|🚚 Delivered to your door · توصيل لحد عندك|💬 Order on WhatsApp · اطلب على واتساب'
  assign item_list = items | split: '|'
-%}

<div class="sahha-mq" role="region" aria-label="Store highlights">
  {%- comment -%}
    Two identical halves; the track translates -50% (= one half), so the loop is
    seamless ONLY if one half is wider than the viewport. The phrase set is short
    (~1300px), so each half repeats the list 3× (~4000px) to clear large/5K
    screens and avoid an empty gap before it loops. Duration scales to match
    (keeps the original ~47px/s scroll speed).
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="sahha-mq__track">
    {%- for half in (1..2) -%}
      {%- for rep in (1..3) -%}
        {%- for item in item_list -%}
          <span class="sahha-mq__item"{% if half == 2 %} aria-hidden="true"{% endif %}>{{ item }}<span class="sahha-mq__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span></span>
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
.sahha-mq { overflow: hidden; border-block: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--paper-2); }
.sahha-mq__track { display: flex; width: max-content; will-change: transform; animation: sahhaMq 84s linear infinite; }
.sahha-mq:hover .sahha-mq__track { animation-play-state: paused; }
.sahha-mq__item { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; padding: 11px 0; font-family: var(--font-body-family); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.312rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--green); white-space: nowrap; }
.sahha-mq__dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); margin-inline: 18px; flex: none; }
@keyframes sahhaMq { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .sahha-mq__track { animation: none; } }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Sahha Marquee",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "sahha-marquee-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "items",
      "label": "Marquee phrases",
      "info": "Separate each phrase with a vertical bar  |  . Mix English and Arabic freely.",
      "default": "🌿 100% verified originals · بضاعة أصلية مضمونة|🇬🇧 Directly sourced from Europe · من أوروبا|🚚 Delivered to your door · توصيل لحد عندك|💬 Order on WhatsApp · اطلب على واتساب"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Sahha Marquee" }]
}
{% endschema %}
